500|$|In December 2009, Kill Rock Stars {{announced}} that it had obtained the rights to re-release <b>Roman</b> <b>Candle</b> and From a Basement on the Hill, originally released by Cavity Search and ANTI-, respectively. <b>Roman</b> <b>Candle</b> would be remastered by Larry Crane. Along with the press release, Kill Rock Stars posted a previously unreleased track of Smith's, titled [...] "Cecilia/Amanda", as a free download. <b>Roman</b> <b>Candle</b> and From a Basement on the Hill were re-released on April 6, 2010, in the US.|$|E
